# Normalize line endings: store text as LF, check out LF on every platform.
# Without this, core.autocrlf=true checks sources out as CRLF on Windows, so
# build.py concatenates a mixed-EOL deliverable that diverges from the LF blob
# (a phantom git-dirty diff + a fresh-clone build_integrity failure). eol=lf
# keeps the working tree LF so the build is byte-reproducible everywhere.
* text=auto eol=lf
